views.markdown: If you need help with "Rainbow CC Switches", you can contact Yoshi Chill, the developer, via e-mail.
Yoshi Chill is the maintainer of the package "Rainbow CC Switches". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Yoshi's repo" repo, Yoshi Chill.
